data.description: Come and view this spacious town house with open concept. Welcome into the nice size entry foyer to the spacious lower level that leads to a leveled backyard.  The open middle level has an eat in kitchen with recess lights, granite counter tops and updated appliances.  The owner suite has a super tub, dual vanities, walk in closet and separate shower.  This home features two nice sizes room with the laundry on the upper level.   Great natural lighting and more.
